@ThinkingandTinkering I'm so glad you made the effort and have a big enough heart to do it and keep doing it, as you say, inspiring one child is enough! 

For me, the water motor wins because the kid improvised all of that himself, out of various rubbish and scrap bits, his comment about the valves was very honest, he basically admitted that "its throwing water everywhere because i made these valves myself" (paraphrased!). 

